<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">Fishing for Bingos</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">Scrabble Words Finder · Quiz · Dictionary</p>


      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-15">June 15, 2026</time>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600"></span>
        <span>8 min read</span>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">A bingo — using all seven tiles for a 50-point bonus — swings games. But bingos don't happen by accident at the expert level. They're engineered through deliberate rack management: playing small now to set up big later. This is the art of fishing.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
